      <title>巴斯克盟友在西班牙投票中打成平手，桑切斯成为拥王者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/sanchez-becomes-kingmaker-as-basque-allies-tie-in-spanish-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个巴斯克民族主义政党在西班牙北部地区的立法选举中并列获胜，总理佩德罗·桑切斯的第三位社会党成为了国王的拥护者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/sanchez-becomes-kingmaker-as-basque-allies-tie-in-spanish-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 20:54:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨对德国经济持乐观态度，理由是通胀和就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨对德国的经济前景持乐观态度，他表示，由于能源成本下降，就业率创历史新高，通胀放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
